text: Martin Svoboda (born 26 April 1975) is a Czech rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague Category:Coxswains (rowing)
